cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language models and cross-lingual transfer. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training models to improve performance. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves improving the performance of language models. It could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as some of the experiments involve image classification. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves training neural networks.
